{"tid":509551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斯諾登協助開發手機App'Haven'　幫維權人士保護資料私隱","createTime":"2017-12-25T12:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T06:47:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fc455ebaa8bc5dc9d495945682262a53ac1bc069","tid":509551,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T12:29:30.000Z","msg":"斯諾登不怕打壓，搵到新工寫手機App！曾經在 2013 年公開美國機密資料而流亡海外的國防技術承包商斯諾登，開發了一款可為用戶保障個人私隱的手機 App，發揮他的專長繼續為網民服務，也不怕無飯開。<br />\n<br />\n斯諾登（Edward Snowden）在一個影片中公佈他協助開發的一款名為「Haven」的手機 App。利用 Android 手機，感應住所、酒店房間的變化。如果在事主出門後，房間曾有人進入，又或者移動過手機，Haven 可以拍照、錄音，記錄手機光學、加速感應器的變化，亦可以向另一部手機發出通知。用戶只要把手機放在隨行的手提電腦上，就可防止該電腦被隨意進入房間內的人打開。<br />\n<br />\n這款 App 是新聞自由基金會（Freedom of Press Foundation）與保衛者計劃（Guardian Project）所聯合開發。斯諾登指出，他開發這款 App 目的是為了保護維權人士的電腦以及住所的保安。但相信非維權人士，都有很多場合可用到他這次開發的 App。<br />\n<br />\n在網路上有網民讚揚斯諾登，指他發揮了自己的專長為維權人士服務，但同時亦有人仍然不相信斯諾登。目前斯諾登本人仍住在俄羅斯接受政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n現時 Google Play 商店已提供「Haven」的測試版下載，如果你信得過他，又有需要的話不妨一試。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/202910_b69bbf7954c49ef1025d50985cbae7f1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F202910_b69bbf7954c49ef1025d50985cbae7f1.png&h=4fbaafb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/202913_8722761ed7e44114f881d3cd00ce3ce4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F202913_8722761ed7e44114f881d3cd00ce3ce4.png&h=d2ef7934&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/25/202914_852adf5fdb6b21e0841d0f3ae0ee2232.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F25%2F202914_852adf5fdb6b21e0841d0f3ae0ee2232.jpeg&h=fde5d51e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHaven 測試版下載：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.havenapp.main\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dorg.havenapp.main&d=TgWdnpomXLMMiI6KIUtHPf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9a1ef16b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.havenapp.main</a><br />\n<br />\nHaven 官方網站：<a href=\"https://guardianproject.github.io/haven/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fguardianproject.github.io%2Fhaven%2F&d=TgWdnpomXLMMiI6KIUtHPf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=12f55f10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://guardianproject.github.io/haven/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：The Verge<br />\n<br />\n有片介紹：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/12/24/snowdenapp/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F12%2F24%2Fsnowdenapp%2Fsoftware%2F&d=TgWdnpomXLMMiI6KIUtHPf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2c26c537\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/12/24/snowdenapp/software/</a>"},{"pid":"a697c71bcc81191b3dd040d337421c629a4d90d7","tid":509551,"uid":61882,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T12:52:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">目前斯諾登本人仍住在俄羅斯接受政治庇護。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://memegenerator.net/img/instances/500x/63057962/i-smell-something-fishy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmemegenerator.net%2Fimg%2Finstances%2F500x%2F63057962%2Fi-smell-something-fishy.jpg&h=c27b188c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f286b0f17b184dfa5cac9fa57e7501fe681ca336","tid":509551,"uid":123264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a697c71bcc81191b3dd040d337421c629a4d90d7","tid":509551,"uid":61882,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T12:52:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">目前斯諾登本人仍住在俄羅斯接受政治庇護。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://memegenerator.net/img/instances/500x/63057962/i-smell-something-fishy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmemegenerator.net%2Fimg%2Finstances%2F500x%2F63057962%